                           Project 2 - Basic chips in Hardware.
                           ----------------------- 

Submitted Files
---------------
README - this file.
ALU.hdl - the ALU chip performing the various functions
Add16.hdl - Adds two 16-bit values the most significant carry bit is ignored.
EqZero16.hdl - checks whether all the bits are zero, plus if the most significant bit is on.
EqZero4.hdl - an assisting chip that checks whether 4-bit number is zero.
FullAdder.hdl - Computes the sum of three bits.
HalfAdder.hdl - Computes the sum of two bits.
Inc16.hdl - 16-bit incrementer.

Remarks
-------
* No special comments.
